Alembic migrations for the Paris United Group Holding backend.

Common commands (run from /backend):

    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add users table"
    alembic upgrade head
    alembic downgrade -1
    alembic history --verbose
    alembic current

Phase 1 ships without any concrete migrations; later phases add tables
under app/models/ which Alembic will autogenerate against.
